claim.claim-text:
2. The method for operating a remote station of claim 1 further comprising the steps of: 
storing the Radio Link Protocol (RLP) state associated with the active data session of said traffic mode; 
storing the traffic channel configuration associated with said traffic mode; 
storing the encryption variables associated with said traffic mode; 
utilizing the stored RLP state, the stored traffic channel configuration, and the stored encryption variables for the transmission and reception of traffic after receiving a channel assignment message on said paging channel.
